title: Hour 2 - NIL Escalation, Cooper Kupp

Dan talks about Ohio State HC Ryan Day's comments regarding the cost of doing business in the new NIL world of the NCAA. And Super Bowl LVI MVP Cooper Kupp drops by and chimes in on Aaron Donald.
